fields.title: Dune: Part 2
fields.description: Paul Atreides unites with Chani and the Fremen while seeking revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone
fields.description: An orphaned boy enrolls in a school of wizardry, where he learns the truth about himself, his family and the terrible evil that haunts the magical world.

fields.title: The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies
fields.description: Bilbo Baggins and company are forced to engage in a war against an array of combatants and keep the Lonely Mountain from falling into the hands of a rising darkness.

fields.title: TheLord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
fields.description: A meek Hobbit from the Shire and eight companions set out on a journey to destroy the powerful One Ring and save Middle-earth from the Dark Lord Sauron.
